1
00:00:00,166 --> 00:00:01,200
hello everyone

2
00:00:01,600 --> 00:00:04,166
today we woke up confined on a floating island

3
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:06,800
but since there's a tree with us

4
00:00:06,966 --> 00:00:09,666
we can use that to expand our landscape

5
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,300
not satisfied with the wood parquet

6
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:15,666
we started moving around the dirt to extract some stones

7
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:18,100
but those rocks were too rough

8
00:00:18,366 --> 00:00:20,766
so we sifted out the various sizes

9
00:00:21,100 --> 00:00:23,533
and it was then that we found some minerals

10
00:00:23,900 --> 00:00:26,366
we used those to build some spinning machines

11
00:00:26,866 --> 00:00:28,500
leading to a steam revolution

12
00:00:28,900 --> 00:00:31,900
we further improved our technology with electricity

13
00:00:32,066 --> 00:00:34,900
to the point of making an Electric Blast Furnace

14
00:00:35,333 --> 00:00:37,633
and to further speed up our progression

15
00:00:37,633 --> 00:00:39,166
we automated everything

16
00:00:39,166 --> 00:00:42,000
from wood collection to a to auto crafting

17
00:00:42,366 --> 00:00:44,566
and now that we automated automation

18
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:46,533
we can quickly dash through HV

19
00:00:46,533 --> 00:00:49,366
and build a clean room for the EV machinery

20
00:00:50,100 --> 00:00:51,300
to power all of that

21
00:00:51,366 --> 00:00:53,400
we built a couple of Steam Turbines

22
00:00:54,166 --> 00:00:56,733
then we processed our mineral byproducts

23
00:00:56,900 --> 00:00:59,333
enough to collect some tungsten and platinum

24
00:00:59,566 --> 00:01:01,733
allowing us to build the good multiblocks

25
00:01:02,066 --> 00:01:03,166
and on top of that

26
00:01:03,166 --> 00:01:06,566
we also have some perfectly overclocking multiblocks

27
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:09,933
which we are now powering with some Nuclear Reactors

28
00:01:10,933 --> 00:01:13,500
building all of those reactors reminded us that

29
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:16,466
it was time to assemble a Fusion Reactor

30
00:01:16,466 --> 00:01:18,866
however, that didn't look good enough

31
00:01:18,966 --> 00:01:22,366
so we built a Research Station to research a better version

32
00:01:22,766 --> 00:01:26,733
but not even those Fusion Reactors satisfied us

33
00:01:26,733 --> 00:01:28,700
so after building a couple more

34
00:01:28,766 --> 00:01:33,566
we figured out we should invest in more computation power to unlock a better reactor

35
00:01:33,666 --> 00:01:36,066
and talking about plasma hot machines

36
00:01:36,333 --> 00:01:38,466
we should also have a Heat Chamber

37
00:01:38,466 --> 00:01:41,566
which goes side by side with a Mega Blast Furnace

38
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:45,366
but of course nothing shall be taller than our Fusion Tower

39
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:47,800
and after building such a long thing

40
00:01:47,933 --> 00:01:49,933
we can chill with some BBC

41
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:52,500
once everything is cool enough

42
00:01:52,566 --> 00:01:55,766
we then start vibrating like a strobe laser

43
00:01:55,766 --> 00:01:59,266
finally, once we realize how awful those jokes were

44
00:01:59,333 --> 00:02:02,733
we build a dimensional finder to find a place to hide

45
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:05,700
such place wasn't behind our new toys

46
00:02:05,866 --> 00:02:10,166
but a new dimension which can only be reached by playing with those long enough

47
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:13,866
however, staring at our latest toy scared us

48
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,533
following our instinct

49
00:02:15,766 --> 00:02:18,666
we built an exponential amount of Fusion Reactors

50
00:02:18,666 --> 00:02:21,933
to obtain the mental fortitude required to try it out

51
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:23,400
with all of that power

52
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:24,966
we turned on its lights

53
00:02:25,566 --> 00:02:28,933
and just when we thought we were done with the DTPF toy

54
00:02:28,933 --> 00:02:30,800
a dark bubble randomly appeared

55
00:02:31,466 --> 00:02:32,766
upon further inspection

56
00:02:32,933 --> 00:02:35,300
it turned out to be some sort of portal

57
00:02:35,366 --> 00:02:37,333
which brought us into a weird temple

58
00:02:37,533 --> 00:02:38,866
this place looked so old

59
00:02:38,866 --> 00:02:41,000
that who built it probably became oil

60
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:43,400
and after extracting said oil

61
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:47,466
we started digging a path into the secret rooms hidden in this place

62
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,933
here we found some ancient technological artifacts

63
00:02:50,933 --> 00:02:52,766
which however seemed to be broken

64
00:02:53,366 --> 00:02:54,866
but more interestingly

65
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:58,933
there was a suspicious device that looked like an elevator that was still working

66
00:02:59,466 --> 00:03:02,400
that device brought us in a room on a familiar corridor

67
00:03:02,666 --> 00:03:05,966
but most interestingly to a Research Station

68
00:03:06,766 --> 00:03:07,666
by using it

69
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:10,466
we figured out how to repair the ancient artifacts

70
00:03:11,066 --> 00:03:13,366
all we needed was some good lubricant

71
00:03:13,366 --> 00:03:15,366
made by (Dutton Common's?) oil

72
00:03:15,533 --> 00:03:17,866
and with the help of some DNA disks

73
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:22,933
we managed to extract the information required to craft the ancient runic circuits

74
00:03:23,533 --> 00:03:25,933
now we can go back on our straight path

75
00:03:25,933 --> 00:03:31,533
and build some new machines that will greatly improve our ability to gather and process materials

76
00:03:31,766 --> 00:03:33,200
to power all of that

77
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:35,500
we tried building new turbines

78
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:38,866
but the Pharaoh curse caused sand to clog those

79
00:03:39,166 --> 00:03:43,000
so we built a supreme turbine that can withstand the sand curse

80
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:46,466
that turbine was also really plasma hungry

81
00:03:46,566 --> 00:03:50,533
so we had to build an auxiliary Fusion Reactor to keep up with it

82
00:03:50,766 --> 00:03:52,600
and after building enough of those

83
00:03:52,766 --> 00:03:57,133
we started playing with some bacteria we found on Tutankhamun body

84
00:03:57,666 --> 00:03:59,166
after enough mutations

85
00:03:59,166 --> 00:04:02,700
we managed to secure a good source of hydrocarbons

86
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:06,133
which we use to build a Runic Manifold Manipulator

87
00:04:06,266 --> 00:04:10,033
this machine will use the product of our newly grown Fusion Reactors

88
00:04:10,033 --> 00:04:14,600
to fold the structure parts required for our new Runic Stargate Assembler

89
00:04:14,900 --> 00:04:17,566
with it, we can restore the ancient Stargate

90
00:04:17,733 --> 00:04:19,733
which will bring us in a dire place

91
00:04:20,133 --> 00:04:22,100
we wandered around for some time

92
00:04:22,333 --> 00:04:24,133
finding all sorts of fluids

93
00:04:24,266 --> 00:04:27,966
but what mostly attracted our curiosity was a Husk of the Flame

94
00:04:28,466 --> 00:04:29,433
after studying it

95
00:04:29,433 --> 00:04:32,200
with the help of some heavily processed nether rack

96
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:34,466
we managed to build a Hell Forge

97
00:04:34,666 --> 00:04:37,300
and while that isn't as good as a God Forge

98
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:40,066
it still produced some quite good plasma

99
00:04:40,100 --> 00:04:43,000
which we cooled down in our new Quantum Chiller

100
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:46,000
but our metalworking still wasn't fast enough

101
00:04:46,466 --> 00:04:49,100
luckily we received a helping hand from the sky

102
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:52,266
that allowed us to build a Mega Alloy Blast Smelter

103
00:04:52,533 --> 00:04:55,100
but now we had too much stuff to cool down

104
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:57,733
and just quantum cooling wasn't good enough

105
00:04:58,133 --> 00:05:01,100
hoping to promote our Vacuum Freezer to Void Freezer

106
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:04,600
we built yet another Stargate towards the end dimension

107
00:05:04,733 --> 00:05:07,133
where we started collecting gas as usual

108
00:05:07,466 --> 00:05:11,266
we then proceeded into a quick expedition to locate a dragon head

109
00:05:11,366 --> 00:05:14,800
which we used to research our new Draconic Infusion Array

110
00:05:15,333 --> 00:05:18,100
with this we can now upgrade our technology

111
00:05:18,366 --> 00:05:22,200
such as the 48 blocks range Wireless Power Transmitter

112
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:25,700
which not only allows us to use wireless energy

113
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:27,533
but also 64 amps hatches

114
00:05:28,133 --> 00:05:31,700
we also gained access to the next tier of Fusion Reactors

115
00:05:31,966 --> 00:05:33,600
but most importantly

116
00:05:33,866 --> 00:05:37,000
we can now make a room that is cleaner than a Sterile Room

117
00:05:37,366 --> 00:05:40,933
this room is indeed filled with the breath of an ancient dragon

118
00:05:41,133 --> 00:05:44,766
allowing for the crafting of the highest level of draconian technology

119
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:49,800
which will culminate with the second tier of Auxiliary Boosted Fusion Reactor

120
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:52,266
capable of producing maxwellium

121
00:05:52,466 --> 00:05:57,666
and after quickly crafting all the parts required for the structure of that new machine

122
00:05:57,866 --> 00:06:00,666
we finally completed it and obtained a new friend

123
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,766
since he's going to stick with us for a while

124
00:06:03,933 --> 00:06:06,766
we pick him up so that we can show his new home

125
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:10,400
this is the place where bad boys get corrected

126
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:12,766
this is where we craft hot fluids

127
00:06:13,066 --> 00:06:15,266
this is where we craft hotter fluids

128
00:06:15,533 --> 00:06:18,000
this is where we craft hot solids

129
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,800
next to it, we cool down the hot materials

130
00:06:21,266 --> 00:06:22,733
those are our assembly lines

131
00:06:23,466 --> 00:06:24,966
this is our main battery

132
00:06:25,100 --> 00:06:27,866
the supreme turbines that charge our batteries

133
00:06:28,366 --> 00:06:30,766
random machines doing passive processes

134
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:34,366
random machines crafting whatever we need

135
00:06:34,366 --> 00:06:34,933
your Mama

136
00:06:35,666 --> 00:06:36,366
expensive

137
00:06:36,666 --> 00:06:38,866
ruins of the old Fusion Reactors

138
00:06:39,266 --> 00:06:40,200
your siblings

139
00:06:40,466 --> 00:06:42,733
and that's your new playground

140
00:06:42,733 --> 00:06:46,666
please be careful and don't twist the fabric of space time

141
00:00:00,166 --> 00:00:01,200
大家好

142
00:00:01,600 --> 00:00:04,166
今天我们在一座空岛上醒来

143
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:06,800
但既然身边还有一棵树

144
00:00:06,966 --> 00:00:09,666
我们就能靠它来扩展地盘

145
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,300
我对木地板不太满意

146
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:15,666
我们开始把泥土搬来搬去，从中得到一些石头

147
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:18,100
但这些石头太粗糙了

148
00:00:18,366 --> 00:00:20,766
所以我们把它们按不同尺寸筛分出来

149
00:00:21,100 --> 00:00:23,533
然后我们从中发现了一些矿物

150
00:00:23,900 --> 00:00:26,366
我们用这些造了几台会转的机器

151
00:00:26,866 --> 00:00:28,500
引发了一场蒸汽革命

152
00:00:28,900 --> 00:00:31,900
我们又用电力进一步提升科技

153
00:00:32,066 --> 00:00:34,900
甚至造出了电高炉

154
00:00:35,333 --> 00:00:37,633
为了进一步加快进度

155
00:00:37,633 --> 00:00:39,166
我们把所有任务都自动化了

156
00:00:39,166 --> 00:00:42,000
从伐木到自动合成

157
00:00:42,366 --> 00:00:44,566
现在我们做完了自动化

158
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:46,533
我们能速通 HV 阶段

159
00:00:46,533 --> 00:00:49,366
并为 EV 机器建一间超净间

160
00:00:50,100 --> 00:00:51,300
为了给这一切供能

161
00:00:51,366 --> 00:00:53,400
我们造了几台蒸汽涡轮机

162
00:00:54,166 --> 00:00:56,733
然后处理矿物副产

163
00:00:56,900 --> 00:00:59,333
最终获得了钨和铂

164
00:00:59,566 --> 00:01:01,733
然后就能造出一些不错的多方块机器

165
00:01:02,066 --> 00:01:03,166
此外

166
00:01:03,166 --> 00:01:06,566
我们还有一些能够完美超频的多方块机器

167
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:09,933
现在正用核反应堆为它们供电

168
00:01:10,933 --> 00:01:13,500
造完这些反应堆让我们想到

169
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:16,466
该组装聚变反应堆了

170
00:01:16,466 --> 00:01:18,866
不过那样看起来还不够体面

171
00:01:18,966 --> 00:01:22,366
所以我们建了一座研究站来研究更好的版本

172
00:01:22,766 --> 00:01:26,733
但就连那些聚变反应堆也没能让我们满意

173
00:01:26,733 --> 00:01:28,700
于是，在又造了几座之后

174
00:01:28,766 --> 00:01:33,566
我们意识到应该投入更多算力，去解锁更好的反应堆

175
00:01:33,666 --> 00:01:36,066
说到等离子体温度的机器

176
00:01:36,333 --> 00:01:38,466
我们也该有一个加热室

177
00:01:38,466 --> 00:01:41,566
旁边摆上一台巨高炉

178
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:45,366
当然，没有什么能比我们的聚变塔更高

179
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:47,800
把这么长的一座东西造出来之后

180
00:01:47,933 --> 00:01:49,933
我们就能享受一下大格调了

181
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:52,500
等一切都冷却下来

182
00:01:52,566 --> 00:01:55,766
我们开始像夜店的灯一样振动

183
00:01:55,766 --> 00:01:59,266
最后，当我们意识到那些笑话有多烂

184
00:01:59,333 --> 00:02:02,733
我们就建造了一台维度探测器，去找个地方躲起来

185
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:05,700
躲藏的地方并不在我们新玩具后面

186
00:02:05,866 --> 00:02:10,166
而是在一个新的维度里，只有游戏时长足够才能前往

187
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:13,866
不过，看着我们的最新玩具，我们感到些许害怕

188
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,533
于是顺着直觉

189
00:02:15,766 --> 00:02:18,666
我们造出了指数级数量的聚变反应堆

190
00:02:18,666 --> 00:02:21,933
来获得尝试进入新维度所需的心理承受力

191
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:23,400
有了这些电力

192
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:24,966
我们把它点亮了

193
00:02:25,566 --> 00:02:28,933
就在我们以为已经把这个 DTPF 玩具折腾完了的时候

194
00:02:28,933 --> 00:02:30,800
一个黑色气泡突然出现

195
00:02:31,466 --> 00:02:32,766
再仔细一看

196
00:02:32,933 --> 00:02:35,300
原来那是某种传送门

197
00:02:35,366 --> 00:02:37,333
把我们带进了一座奇怪的神庙

198
00:02:37,533 --> 00:02:38,866
这地方看上去太古老了

199
00:02:38,866 --> 00:02:41,000
建造它的人大概都已经化成石油了

200
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:43,400
提取完那些石油之后

201
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:47,466
我们开始开凿通往这里的密室的通路

202
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,933
在那我们发现了一些古代科技遗物

203
00:02:50,933 --> 00:02:52,766
不过它们看起来似乎都坏了

204
00:02:53,366 --> 00:02:54,866
但更有意思的是

205
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:58,933
这里还有一个看起来像电梯，却仍在运作的可疑装置

206
00:02:59,466 --> 00:03:02,400
那台装置把我们带到了熟悉走廊上的一个房间

207
00:03:02,666 --> 00:03:05,966
更准确地说，是一座研究站

208
00:03:06,766 --> 00:03:07,666
通过使用它

209
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:10,466
我们弄清了如何修复这些古代遗物

210
00:03:11,066 --> 00:03:13,366
我们只需要一些好润滑剂

211
00:03:13,366 --> 00:03:15,366
由 Dutton Common 的油制成

212
00:03:15,533 --> 00:03:17,866
再加上一些 DNA 光盘的帮助

213
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:22,933
我们就提取出了制作古代符文电路板所需的信息

214
00:03:23,533 --> 00:03:25,933
现在我们可以回到正轨了

215
00:03:25,933 --> 00:03:31,533
造一些新机器，大幅提升我们采集和处理材料的能力

216
00:03:31,766 --> 00:03:33,200
为了给这一切供能

217
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:35,500
我们尝试建造新的涡轮机

218
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:38,866
但法老的诅咒让沙子把它们堵住了

219
00:03:39,166 --> 00:03:43,000
所以我们造了一台能扛住沙之诅咒的至尊涡轮机

220
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:46,466
那台涡轮机也非常吃等离子体

221
00:03:46,566 --> 00:03:50,533
所以我们不得不造一台辅助聚变堆来跟上它的消耗

222
00:03:50,766 --> 00:03:52,600
在造了足够的机器之后

223
00:03:52,766 --> 00:03:57,133
我们开始研究在图坦卡蒙遗体上发现的细菌

224
00:03:57,666 --> 00:03:59,166
经过足够多的变异

225
00:03:59,166 --> 00:04:02,700
我们终于弄到了一种不错的碳氢化合物来源

226
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:06,133
我们用它来造了一台符文流形操纵者

227
00:04:06,266 --> 00:04:10,033
这台机器消耗我们新建的聚变堆的产物

228
00:04:10,033 --> 00:04:14,600
来折叠出符文星门组装机所需的结构部件

229
00:04:14,900 --> 00:04:17,566
有了它，我们就能修复古老的星门

230
00:04:17,733 --> 00:04:19,733
把我们带到一个更糟的地方

231
00:04:20,133 --> 00:04:22,100
我们四处游荡了一会

232
00:04:22,333 --> 00:04:24,133
寻找各种各样的流体

233
00:04:24,266 --> 00:04:27,966
但最吸引我们好奇心的是烈焰空壳

234
00:04:28,466 --> 00:04:29,433
研究它之后

235
00:04:29,433 --> 00:04:32,200
再加上一些经过重度处理的下界岩

236
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:34,466
我们成功造出了狱火锻炉

237
00:04:34,666 --> 00:04:37,300
虽然它不如神之锻炉那么好

238
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:40,066
但仍然能产出相当不错的等离子体

239
00:04:40,100 --> 00:04:43,000
我们用新的量子冷却器冷却等离子体

240
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:46,000
但我们的金属加工速度还是不够快

241
00:04:46,466 --> 00:04:49,100
幸运的是，有高人伸出援手

242
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:52,266
这让我们得以造出巨型合金冶炼炉

243
00:04:52,533 --> 00:04:55,100
但这样要冷却的东西太多了

244
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:57,733
单靠量子冷却已经不够

245
00:04:58,133 --> 00:05:01,100
我们希望把真空冷冻机升级成虚空冷冻机

246
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:04,600
于是又建了一座通往末地的星门

247
00:05:04,733 --> 00:05:07,133
在那里我们照例开始收集气体

248
00:05:07,466 --> 00:05:11,266
然后我们快速找到一个龙首

249
00:05:11,366 --> 00:05:14,800
并用它来研究新的龙芯灌注阵列

250
00:05:15,333 --> 00:05:18,100
有了它，我们现在可以升级科技了

251
00:05:18,366 --> 00:05:22,200
比如 48 格范围无线供电发射器

252
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:25,700
它不仅让我们能使用无线能源

253
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:27,533
还支持 64 A 能源仓

254
00:05:28,133 --> 00:05:31,700
我们也解锁了下一等级的聚变反应堆

255
00:05:31,966 --> 00:05:33,600
但最重要的是

256
00:05:33,866 --> 00:05:37,000
我们现在可以造出比无菌室还干净的房间

257
00:05:37,366 --> 00:05:40,933
这间房间里确实充满了远古巨龙之息

258
00:05:41,133 --> 00:05:44,766
这使我们能够打造最高级的龙族科技

259
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:49,800
最终变成二阶辅助增强聚变反应堆

260
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:52,266
它能够产出麦克斯韦合金

261
00:05:52,466 --> 00:05:57,666
在快速制作完那台新机器结构所需的全部零件后

262
00:05:57,866 --> 00:06:00,666
我们终于把它造好了，还获得了一位新朋友

263
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,766
既然他要跟我们待一阵子

264
00:06:03,933 --> 00:06:06,766
我们把他抱起来，好带他看看新家

265
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:10,400
这里是坏孩子接受矫正的地方

266
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:12,766
这里是我们制造热流体的地方

267
00:06:13,066 --> 00:06:15,266
这里是我们制造更热的流体的地方

268
00:06:15,533 --> 00:06:18,000
这里是我们制造热固体的地方

269
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,800
我们在旁边把这些热材料冷却下来

270
00:06:21,266 --> 00:06:22,733
那些是我们的装配线

271
00:06:23,466 --> 00:06:24,966
这是我们的主电池

272
00:06:25,100 --> 00:06:27,866
为电池充电的至尊涡轮机

273
00:06:28,366 --> 00:06:30,766
负责被动产线的路人机器

274
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:34,366
负责制造我们需要的一切的路人机器

275
00:06:34,366 --> 00:06:34,933
你妈

276
00:06:35,666 --> 00:06:36,366
贵

277
00:06:36,666 --> 00:06:38,866
聚变反应堆旧址

278
00:06:39,266 --> 00:06:40,200
你的兄弟姐妹

279
00:06:40,466 --> 00:06:42,733
那里是你的新游乐场

280
00:06:42,733 --> 00:06:46,666
小心，不要扭曲了时空的结构

281
00:07:00,633 --> 00:07:04,566
（我忍不住要加上这个）

